{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "在昆仑山白石大屋中，绿袍人、红衫小鬼和灰白色纸扎轿子相继到来。白棉布苦行僧揭示了飞蛾行动的目标人物：林还恩，21岁，林还玉的孪生兄弟，因全身血络经脉混乱被选为诱饵。绿袍人与使用乌金丝悬浮空中的黑衣人展开激战，苦行僧用纯钢唧筒喷出金色水雾黏附在乌金丝上引发大火。黑衣人被火困住后，红小鬼挣脱身上铁板束缚，化身鬼魅般割下了黑衣人的头颅。然而割头小鬼此番没有先割头，反而抱住了从绿袍中蜕变出的赤裸长腿美女，在她腿上咬了一口后才离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "你不该来，为什么要来?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "为什么我不能来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "你说我不该来，是不是因为我把不该来的人带来了?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "我也知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "如果不是我，纸扎店的那些人，永远都找不到这里。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "也就因为一点，所以我才一定要来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "我不来，他们怎么会找到这里来?他们不来，怎么会死在这里?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "有你在这里，他们来了，怎么能活着回去?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "他们是不是能活着回去，跟我在不在这里没有关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "那么跟谁有关系?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "text": "他们是不是能活着回去，只跟你有关系，因为他们是你带来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍人",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "他们是我带来的，当然应该由我打发。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰、砰、砰，请开门。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是丁小弟。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来借小刀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "劈竹子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "做蒸笼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蒸人头。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送给老妈当点心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "你这次来，不是为了急着要知道这次行动的结果?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "当然不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "你也不想知道楚留香的生死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "我当然想知道，只不过我早就知道了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "你知道了什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "飞蛾行动开始，楚留香就已死了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "他不来，早已死。他来，还是死。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "那么你这次来，还是等着来割头的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "现在已经有头可割，你还不快去?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "谁的头?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "你早已想割的那个头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "红小鬼",
      "listener": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "text": "那王八蛋的头现在已经可以去割了?",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_xing_seng",
      "speaker_name": "苦行僧",
      "listener": "char_ge_tou_xiao_gui",
      "text": "好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    }
